From: Hien Huynh <hien.huynh.px@renesas.com>
Date: Wed, 4 Mar 2020 14:07:07 +0700
Subject: [PATCH 203/268] arm64: dts: renesas: r8a774b1: Add watchdog node

This patch adds watchdog node for RZ/G2N (R8A774B1) SoC.

Signed-off-by: hoahuynh <hoa.huynh.ud@renesas.com>
Signed-off-by: Hien Huynh <hien.huynh.px@renesas.com>
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/renesas/r8a774b1.dtsi | 7 ++++++-
 1 file changed, 6 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/renesas/r8a774b1.dtsi b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/renesas/r8a774b1.dtsi
index 4931c5c..ca41ba0 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/renesas/r8a774b1.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/renesas/r8a774b1.dtsi
@@ -160,8 +160,13 @@
 		ranges;
 
 		rwdt: watchdog@e6020000 {
+			compatible = "renesas,r8a774b1-wdt",
+					"renesas,rcar-gen3-wdt";
 			reg = <0 0xe6020000 0 0x0c>;
-			/* placeholder */
+			clocks = <&cpg CPG_MOD 402>;
+			power-domains = <&sysc R8A774B1_PD_ALWAYS_ON>;
+			resets = <&cpg 402>;
+			status = "disabled";
 		};
 
 		gpio0: gpio@e6050000 {
